
LANGUAGE KEY WORDS
------------------
and - logical conjunction
at - for temporal qualifiers
for - looping
in - for contains
is - for type matching
mod - modulo operator
not - logical negation
o - "bullet" for bulleted list of value options
or - logical disjunction
otherwise - default value in a list of options
step - delta in a range
$value - the current context within a type constraint
when - for pattern matching
where - for a precomputed context shown after an expression
within - for a precomputed context shown before an expression


PREDEFINED STRING LITERAL FUNCTIONS
-----------------------------------
lligne-code(code: String)   // For code generation
time(isoTime: String)       // For instants
units(units: String)        // For units of measure